{"word":"δωρεάν","slug":"δωρεάν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>δωρεάν</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ acc.\">acc.</a> of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δωρεά\">δωρεά</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> <b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘being freely given/without charge’, <b><i>freely</i></b> = the positive aspect <b><i>for nothing</i> <a href='B:470 10:8'>Mt 10:8</a>; <a href='B:520 3:24'>Ro 3:24</a>; <a href='B:540 11:7'>2 Cor 11:7</a>; <a href='B:600 3:8'>2 Th 3:8</a>; <a href='B:730 21:6'>Rv 21:6</a>; <a href='B:730 22:17'>22:17</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘being without purpose’, <b><i>in vain</i></b> = the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ neg.\">neg.</a> aspect <b><i>for nothing</i> <a href='B:550 2:21'>Gal 2:21</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp></b> ‘being undeserved’, <b><i>without cause</i> <a href='B:500 15:25'>J 15:25</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:δωρεά\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:δωρέομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}